Package: rdcqr
Type: Package
Title: Local Composite Quantile Regression Method for Regression Discontinuity
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2020-08-31
Author: Xiao Huang
Maintainer: Xiao Huang <xiao_huang@outlook.com>
Description: This package computes local composite quantile regression estimator
    for the treatment effect in both sharp and fuzzy regression discontinuity 
    designs. It also computes the bias-corrected estimator and adjusts its 
    standard error by taking into consideration the variability due to bias
    correction.
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: ks (>= 1.11.7), locfit (>= 1.5-9.1), Rcpp (>= 1.0.2), RcppParallel (>= 5.0.2)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RcppParallel
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
SystemRequirements: GNU make 
URL: https://github.com/xhuang20/rdcqr
BugReports: https://github.com/xhuang20/rdcqr/issues
